==============================================================================
JOB B — is the switch the cell COUNT, or the input FLUCTUATION?
==============================================================================
The 320+80 control is unchanged and must still PASS (that is v4's result).
The 80+20 network is run at connection probabilities that match its per-
pathway CV to the 320+80 network's, so that only N differs. If it now
passes too, the switch was the noise and not the count.

